📖Overview.

The Intense Racing Music Pack is a high-quality collection of music suitable for use in games, movies, animations, and various other projects. This pack consists of 12 tracks that combine elements of electronic music with the thrilling vibe of cyberpunk genre, resulting in unique and captivating compositions. With powerful beats and energetic soundscapes, these tracks effectively complement racing and action scenes, setting the stage for challenging and intense atmospheres.



🕹️Functionality.


  • Fusion of Diverse Genres: This pack combines electronic music and cyberpunk elements to provide distinctive and characterful tracks.
  • High-Quality Sound: All music pieces are professionally crafted by sound designers to ensure exceptional quality.
  • Versatile Use: Suitable for a wide range of projects, including games, movies, animations, and more.
  • Emphasis on Action and Speed: The music is designed to enhance racing and action sequences with its vibrant energy.
